==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Puckery
<hw>Puck"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Producing, or tending to produce, a pucker; <as>as, a
<ex>puckery</ex> taste</as>.</def> <rj><au>Lowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Inclined to become puckered or wrinkled; full of
puckers or wrinkles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Puckfist</ent>⟦br⟧
